name: cred-rea-fish-team-belt-transect-surveys-at-oahu-island-2005
notes: Belt transects along 3 consecutively-placed, 25m transect lines were surveyed as part of Rapid Ecological Assessments conducted at 10 sites at Oahu in July, 2005 from the NOAA vessel Hi'ialakai (HI05-05). Raw survey data included species level abundance estimates.
